Neutral (N) ACD_MOST_ApKa &gt;6.5 and ACD_MOST_BpKa&lt;8.5
Zwitterion (ZW)	ACD_MOST_ApKa &lt;6.5 and ACD_MOST_BpKa&gt;8.5
</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Molecular species at pH 7.4 calculated by ACD/Labs PhysChem software</skos:definition>
